Gopikchr is a pure Go implementation of the PikChr language for describing technical diagrams

The text

    ```pikchr
    fill = mintcream
    box "Hello"
    arrow
    box "World"
    ```

is rendered as:

```pikchr
fill = mintcream
box "Hello"
arrow
box "World"
```

URL: https://github.com/gopikchr/gopikchr

